{
  "info": {
    "name": "Yamecent Admin API",
    "_postman_id": "yamecent-admin-api-collection",
    "description": "Yamecent Admin 後台 API 文件\n\n## 使用流程\n1. 呼叫「登入」取得 token\n2. token 會自動存入 Collection 變數 `token`\n3. 所有受保護端點已預設帶入 `Authorization: Bearer {{token}}`\n4. 呼叫「登出」後 token 立即失效",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://yamecent-admin.local/api",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "登入後自動填入，無需手動修改"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "認證",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "登入",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "var res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.code === 200 && res.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.token);",
                  "    console.log('Token 已儲存：' + res.token);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "account",
                  "value": "testuser",
                  "description": "帳號（必填）",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "password",
                  "value": "secret123",
                  "description": "密碼（必填）",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "會員登入，取得 JWT Token。\n\n登入成功後 **Token 會自動存入 Collection 變數 `token`**，後續受保護端點無需手動複製貼上。\n\n- Token 有效期：7 天（604800 秒，可透過環境變數 `JWT_TTL` 調整）\n- Token 儲存於 Redis，登出後立即失效"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "登入成功",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 200,\n  \"msg\": \"登入成功\",\n  \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n  \"expires_in\": 604800,\n  \"member\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"account\": \"testuser\",\n    \"avatar\": \"/uploads/avatar/20260324/abc123.jpg\",\n    \"nickname\": \"測試用戶\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "帳號或密碼錯誤",
              "status": "Unauthorized",
              "code": 401,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 401,\n  \"msg\": \"帳號或密碼錯誤\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "帳號已停用",
              "status": "Forbidden",
              "code": 403,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 403,\n  \"msg\": \"帳號已停用\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "缺少必填欄位",
              "status": "Unprocessable Entity",
              "code": 422,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 422,\n  \"msg\": \"帳號和密碼不能為空\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "登出",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "var res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', '');",
                  "    console.log('Token 已清除');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/logout",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "logout"]
            },
            "description": "登出並立即撤銷 Token（從 Redis 刪除）。\n\n登出成功後 Collection 變數 `token` 會自動清空。\n\n即使 JWT 本身尚未到期，登出後也無法再使用。"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "登出成功",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 200,\n  \"msg\": \"登出成功\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "未帶 Token",
              "status": "Unauthorized",
              "code": 401,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 401,\n  \"msg\": \"請先登入\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Token 已過期",
              "status": "Unauthorized",
              "code": 401,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 401,\n  \"msg\": \"Token 已過期\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Token 已失效（已登出）",
              "status": "Unauthorized",
              "code": 401,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 401,\n  \"msg\": \"Token 已失效\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "文章",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "取得所有文章",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/articles?type=",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["articles"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "type",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "文章類型篩選（選填）：1 = 一般、2 = 高級、3 = 特級；不傳則回傳全部"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "取得所有上架中的文章列表（is_active = 1），依 ID 倒序排列。\n\n回傳欄位：id, title, image, type, created_at\n\n文章類型：1 = 一般文章、2 = 高級文章、3 = 特級文章\n\n**不需要登入 Token（公開）**\n\n### 可選篩選\n- `type`：按文章類型篩選（1/2/3），不傳則回傳全部類型"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "成功",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 200,\n  \"msg\": \"success\",\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": 1,\n      \"title\": \"文章標題\",\n      \"image\": \"/uploads/article/xxx.jpg\",\n      \"type\": 1,\n      \"created_at\": \"2026-03-24T00:00:00.000000Z\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "取得單篇文章",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/articles/1",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["articles", "1"]
            },
            "description": "依 ID 取得單篇上架文章的完整內容。\n\n文章類型：1 = 一般文章、2 = 高級文章、3 = 特級文章\n\n**不需要登入 Token（公開）**"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "成功",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 200,\n  \"msg\": \"success\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"title\": \"文章標題\",\n    \"image\": \"/uploads/article/xxx.jpg\",\n    \"content\": \"<p>文章內容 HTML</p>\",\n    \"type\": 1,\n    \"is_active\": 1,\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-03-24T00:00:00.000000Z\",\n    \"updated_at\": \"2026-03-24T00:00:00.000000Z\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "文章不存在",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 404,\n  \"msg\": \"文章不存在\",\n  \"data\": null\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "留言",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "取得文章留言",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/articles/1/comments?page=1",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["articles", "1", "comments"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1",
                  "description": "頁碼（選填，預設第 1 頁，每頁 20 筆）"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "取得指定文章的留言列表，依時間新到舊排序。\n\n**不需要登入 Token（公開）**\n\n- 每頁 20 筆，支援分頁\n- 回傳留言人基本資訊（id, nickname, avatar）"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "成功",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 200,\n  \"msg\": \"success\",\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": 5,\n      \"content\": \"這篇文章寫得很好！\",\n      \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T10:00:00.000000Z\",\n      \"admin_reply\": \"感謝您的留言！\",\n      \"admin_replied_at\": \"2026-03-25T12:00:00.000000Z\",\n      \"member\": {\n        \"id\": 1,\n        \"nickname\": \"測試用戶\",\n        \"avatar\": \"/uploads/avatar/20260324/abc123.jpg\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 4,\n      \"content\": \"學到很多，謝謝！\",\n      \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T09:00:00.000000Z\",\n      \"admin_reply\": null,\n      \"admin_replied_at\": null,\n      \"member\": {\n        \"id\": 2,\n        \"nickname\": \"小明\",\n        \"avatar\": null\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"current_page\": 1,\n    \"last_page\": 3,\n    \"per_page\": 20,\n    \"total\": 50\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "文章不存在",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 404,\n  \"msg\": \"文章不存在\",\n  \"data\": null\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "發表留言",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "content",
                  "value": "這篇文章寫得很好！",
                  "description": "留言內容（必填，最多 500 字）",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/articles/1/comments",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["articles", "1", "comments"]
            },
            "description": "對指定文章發表留言。**需要登入 Token**\n\n- 每次留言後需等待 30 秒才能再次留言（冷卻機制）\n- 留言內容最多 500 字"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "留言成功",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 200,\n  \"msg\": \"留言成功\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 6,\n    \"content\": \"這篇文章寫得很好！\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-03-25T10:05:00.000000Z\",\n    \"admin_reply\": null,\n    \"admin_replied_at\": null,\n    \"member\": {\n      \"id\": 1,\n      \"nickname\": \"測試用戶\",\n      \"avatar\": \"/uploads/avatar/20260324/abc123.jpg\"\n    }\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "冷卻中（30 秒限制）",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 429,\n  \"msg\": \"請等待 18 秒後再留言\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"wait_seconds\": 18\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "留言內容為空",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 422,\n  \"msg\": \"留言內容不能為空\",\n  \"data\": null\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "留言內容超過 500 字",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 422,\n  \"msg\": \"留言內容不能超過 500 字\",\n  \"data\": null\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "文章不存在",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 404,\n  \"msg\": \"文章不存在\",\n  \"data\": null\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "帳號已被禁言",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 403,\n  \"msg\": \"您已被禁止留言\",\n  \"data\": null\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "未帶 Token",
              "status": "Unauthorized",
              "code": 401,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"code\": 401,\n  \"msg\": \"請先登入\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "會員",
      "item": [
        {
